modDescription:
Adds a challenging, end-game Raid Boss, [party girl](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-zombies/) Diamond, to the Wastelands. Server-side only – Players do not need to download! It should play nicely with other mods but let me know! You may want to change the xp/coin reward and/or need to tone down the difficulty by reducing the entity health/regen, but see what you think.

We have a ton of other unique, complex enemies on our BlewBarry Farms 7d2d [server](http://www.blewbarryfarms.com/) and we may release more for the community in the coming months! Come see what we have if you don’t want to wait!

**[Download](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1xEZ4kYzJD_pQrcJ1kaoWnT2q8y9diBys/view?usp=sharing)**
